
#RPI RelayBoard
Hardware
- 9-16v/5V 4a Buck Converter - 2 port pluggable phoenix connector
- two ADS1115
-- Waterlevel Sensor, Voltage Divider (1k:?) -> 8 port pluggable phoenix connector
-- Pekaway BatteryShunt -> Rj11 Connector
- Rj45 Connector for Pekaway Touchscreen

Uart1 + Power from the Input Screw Terminal


DS18B20 Port ->  3 port pluggable phoenix connector
OneWire Realtime Clock
4x NO Relay -> 2 port pluggable phoenix connector
4x NC/NO Relay -> 3 port pluggable phoenix connector
JST Connector - "MultiUart" - Uart5 RPI 4